Firebase is a set of backend cloud computing services.
What is Firebase ??
>> Firebase is a product of google which helps developers to build , manage and grow there apps easily.
>> build apps faster and more secure way
>> provides services to web , unity , android and ios
>> Uses NoSql to store the data in database. 
Features of Firebase : 
1. Authentication 
2. Hosting 
3. Storage 
4. Cloud Firestore 
5. FCM (Firebase cloude Messaging )